nd improve CRISPR-Cas mediated gene editing technologies based on prokaryotic CRISPR systems and eukaryotic DNA repair mechanisms.</div></main><footer></footer></section></div><div class="ArticleSummary" data-aos="fade-up"><section class="thumbnail">  <figure class="thumbnailWrapper"><a href="/what-s-your-story-ideas-and-discoveries-worth-sharing-71530" target="_self"><picture><source media="(min-width: 568px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71530/aImg/51697/63777-istock-800x560-jr6-t.webp" type="image/webp"><source media="(min-width: 568px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71530/aImg/51697/63777-istock-800x560-jr6-t.jpg" type="image/jpeg"><source media="(max-width: 400px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71530/aImg/51697/63777-istock-800x560-jr6-s.webp" type="image/webp"><source media="(max-width: 400px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71530/aImg/51697/63777-istock-800x560-jr6-s.jpg" type="image/jpeg"><source media="(max-width: 567px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71530/aImg/51697/63777-istock-800x560-jr6-m.webp" type="image/webp"><source media="(max-width: 567px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71530/aImg/51697/63777-istock-800x560-jr6-m.jpg" type="image/jpeg"><img src="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71530/aImg/51697/63777-istock-800x560-jr6-t.jpg" alt="Conceptual retro image of a man wearing a silly mind reading gadget on his head, holding a pencil, and writing his thoughts down in a notebook." title="Conceptual retro image of a man wearing a silly mind reading gadget on his head, holding a pencil, and writing his thoughts down in a notebook." loading="lazy"></picture></a></figure></section><section class="text flex flex-col"><header><a href="/what-s-your-story-ideas-and-discoveries-worth-sharing-71530" target="_self"><div class="h3 max-2-lines l-h-3">What&#39;s Your Story? Ideas and Discoveries Worth Sharing</div></a></header><main><div class="displayAuthorAndTime"><span class="h6"><em>The Scientist</em> </span><span class="h6"> | Nov 29, 2023</span><span class="h6"> | 3 min read</span></div><div class="max-3-lines l-h-3">A new writing contest provides life scientists with a platform to try their hands at science journalism, tell their science stories, develop their communication skills, and publish their work.</div></main><footer></footer></section></div><div class="ArticleSummary" data-aos="fade-up"><section class="thumbnail">  <figure class="thumbnailWrapper"><a href="/competition-guidelines-and-writing-tips-71529" target="_self"><picture><source media="(min-width: 568px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71529/aImg/51693/63777-istock-800x560-jr5-t.webp" type="image/webp"><source media="(min-width: 568px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71529/aImg/51693/63777-istock-800x560-jr5-t.jpg" type="image/jpeg"><source media="(max-width: 400px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71529/aImg/51693/63777-istock-800x560-jr5-s.webp" type="image/webp"><source media="(max-width: 400px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71529/aImg/51693/63777-istock-800x560-jr5-s.jpg" type="image/jpeg"><source media="(max-width: 567px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71529/aImg/51693/63777-istock-800x560-jr5-m.webp" type="image/webp"><source media="(max-width: 567px)" srcset="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71529/aImg/51693/63777-istock-800x560-jr5-m.jpg" type="image/jpeg"><img src="https://cdn.the-scientist.com/assets/articleNo/71529/aImg/51693/63777-istock-800x560-jr5-t.jpg" alt="Close up image of an open notebook with blank pages, a computer keyboard, and a pen." title="Close up image of an open notebook with blank pages, a computer keyboard, and a pen." loading="lazy"></picture></a></figure></section><section class="text flex flex-col"><header><a href="/competition-g